(7,3,'Dewalt DWS520KT Plunge Cut Circular Saw', 'Dewalt DWS520KT Plunge Saw and Guide Rail, complete with 48 tooth saw blade, 2 x 1.5m guide rail with connectors, carry bag and carrying case. Dewalt offer a simple and effective solution to a wide range of applications including laminate cutting and door trimming. Extremely high levels of accuracy, finish and durability make the DWS520KT a desireable product. Dewalt DWS520KT plunge saw from Dewalt gives outstanding levels of accuracy and finish, as well as extreme durability. The DWS520KT is designed in conjunction with guide rails that are easy to set up and use, the system offers a simple and effective solution for a range of applications, particularly with laminate cutting. The Dewalt DWS520KT has a flat outside guard so can be used for door trimming. Anti kickback function stops the saw from moving backwards along the rail.','https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/nJcAAOSwDtxgYsQM/s-l1600.jpg',210,'active'),
(8,2,'Folding Bike Viking Metropolis 20" Wheel 6 Speed Folder Bicycle White', 'First established in Wolverhampton in 1908 the Viking brand has a history, rich in the tradition of top quality road bikes throughout the century. Quality, style and durability have always been the hallmarks of Viking cycles. Todays Vikings still embody those core qualities, as cycling in the UK has developed Viking has looked to widen its range to meet demands of modern cyclists. Now designed in Manchester the 2018 Viking range includes Road, Gravel, Fixed Wheel, Hybrid, Heritage, Electric Bikes, Folders and Tandems.', 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/6LgAAOSwSMRgSKxi/s-l1600.jpg', 321, 'active'),
